# Financial Control

Financial Control is a full-stack web application designed to help users monitor and manage their personal finances. The application allows users to record income and expenses, create budgets and savings goals, visualize financial data through interactive charts, and monitor spending over time.

This project was developed as a full-stack learning experience using React and native PHP, with a strong focus on software architecture, REST APIs, authentication, and database management.

---

## Features

### User Authentication
- User registration
- Secure login
- JWT (JSON Web Token) authentication
- Protected API endpoints

### Dashboard
- Financial overview
- Monthly statistics
- Spending summaries
- Interactive charts

### Transactions
- Add income and expenses
- View transaction history
- Delete transactions
- Monthly transaction summaries

### Budget Management
- Create budgets
- Define spending limits
- Track budget usage
- Automatic budget percentage calculation

### Financial Goals
- Create savings goals
- Update current progress
- Track completion percentage

### Data Visualization
- Pie Chart
- Bar Chart
- Line Chart
- Radial Progress Chart

### Filtering System
- Filter transactions
- Filter budgets
- Filter goals
- Date range filtering
- Transaction type filtering

### CRUD Operations
The application supports complete Create, Read, Update and Delete operations for:

- Transactions
- Budgets
- Goals

