## Database

The application uses MySQL.

The complete database schema is available in:

```
database.sql
```

Import the file before running the backend.

---

## Installation

### Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/financial-control.git
```

### Frontend

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

### Backend

Configure your database credentials inside the backend configuration files and start your local PHP server.

